  'Transparent pricing with detailed quotes',
  'OE-quality parts with warranty protection',
  'Manufacturer-compliant service procedures',
  'Experienced technicians you can talk to directly',
  'Modern diagnostic equipment and tools',
  'Comfortable waiting area with WiFi',
